since the workers were also major stakeholders.
</P>
<P>
"There is need for workernot be able to participate
in the process," said spokesman of the SAID'99, Elias Mbonini.
</P>
<P>
The labor leaders said ti said the governments should also show political w
l
and provide finance so that the process was successful.
</P>
<P>
The spokesman also said there was need for the integration
between labor ministries in the region as they served the sameof all
partners. 
