<HEADLINE> Tunis Stock Exchange Index Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TUNIS, October 5 (Xinhua) -- The Tunis Stock Exchange index
closed at 740.97 points Tuesday, up 1.34 percent from Monday's
finish.
</P>
<P>
A daily bulletin of the bourse said 201,527 shares changed
hands in 1,013 deals, and the turnover was 4,114,327 dinars (3.7
million U.S. dollars). 
</P>
</TEXT>
