 imperative for researchers to come up with other new crop
varieties that are more resistant to drought and pests, adding
that with the shared knowledge from Kenyan scientists the work was
going to be easy.
</P>
<P>
"Zimbabwe has been experiencing droughts in the past years and
it is important that new drought resistant crops are invented to
ensure better yields," Gopo said.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, participants at the workshop have said farmers
should be included in these research projects so that they would
also know how research is done and also be able to do research
work on their own.  
