Bihari Vajpayee Wednesday beat his Congress rival Karan Singh by
123,624 votes, winning his seat in the Lucknow constituency in
North India's Uttar Pradesh state.
</P>
<P>
This was the fourth time he won the seat in Lucknow. He had won
the seat thrice in a row in 1991, 1996 and 1998.
