<HEADLINE> Project Agreements At Chinese Technology Fair </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHENZHEN, October 6 (Xinhua) -- There were 15 project
agreements, worth nearly 1.45 billion yuan (175 million U.S.
dollars), signed today at China's first International High
Technology Fair in the southern city of Shenzhen.
</P>
<P>
