Patrick MicGovern, the CEO of International Digital Group said
that they will invest 46 million yuan in two communications and
computer network projects. The group also plans to invest 100
million U.S. dollars in a risk investment fund in China.
</P>
<P>
More than 10 signing ceremonies will be held during the five-
day fair, providing opportunities for Chinese universities,
research institutes, enterprises, and international companies to
find cooperative partners.  
</P>
