cents to end at 10.50 Singapore dollars. StarCru retreated 20
cents to close at 5.80 Singapore dollars. Creative 50, JIT and
NatElec each dipped 10 cents to finish at 18.00, 3.08 and 7.10
Singapore dollars respectively.
</P>
