<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, October 6 (Xinhua) -- The BJP-led alliance was
surging ahead, winning 11 of the 15 Lok Sabha seats and leading
136 of 246 constituencies from which trends were available at 1530
local time Wednesday.
</P>
