<HEADLINE> Nepal Opens Greeting System on Internet </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KATHMANDU October 6 (Xinhua) -- Nepal Home Page, one of the
popular website for information and links related to Nepal, has
opened an electronic greeting card system that enables users to
send and receive electronic greetings to and from any person on
the Internet, The Kathmandu Post reported Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
The paper said that this system has been brought up for
upcoming Dashain and Tihar festivals which falls on October 16-24.
</P>
<P>
The Nepal Home Page is designed and maintained by the Yomari
Information Center of Nepal. 
</P>
