<TEXT>
<P>
KATHMANDU, October 6 (Xinhua) -- Qatar Airways launched
Adventure Club designed to provide Kathmandu-bound passengers with
special discounts on their holidays to Nepal at no extra costs,
The Kathmandu Post reported Wednesday.
</P>
