when the verdict of the 13th Lok Sabha election hidden in the
ballot boxes was revealed.
</P>
<P>
According to the Election Commission, results for 45
constituencies, where voting was held through electronic machines,
will be declared by Wednesday afternoon and early trends will be
available as early as nine o'clock.
</P>
