Home Minister L. K. Advani.
</P>
<P>
Trends of constituencies, where polling was held by the
traditional method, will be available by late afternoon and
results of all constituencies will be announced by late evening on
October 7.
</P>
<P>
The 13th Lok Sabha will be constituted on October 10 with the
Election Commission submitting the list of newly-elected members
to President K. R. Narayanan.
</P>
<P>
The new government will be formed and a session of the Lok
Sabha will be called by October 20, as laid down by the Indian
constitution. 
