The grant is very important for Cambodian government to reform
its power sector to make it more competitive and effective, Suy
Sem said.
</P>
<P>
The French government has financed about 10 million U.S.
dollars for joint Electricite du Cambodge and Electricite de
France projects in the last 10 years. 
