At the opening ceremony, which opened in Montevideo on Tuesday,
Uruguayan President Julio Sanguinetti and Organization of American
States Secretary-General Cesar Gaviria stressed the importance of
the joint efforts and shared responsibilities of all countries on
this continent in combating drugs.
</P>
<P>
